data.description: *ASK AGENT ABOUT INCENTIVES ON THIS HOME!*  Highly sought after floor plan, situated on a large lot also features a 3 car garage and extended driveway. Everything you need for your toys or the kids' cars! Inside, updated flooring and accents make you feel at home. Boasts a grand great room open to the kitchen but also has versatility in flex space for the whole family to have their needs. Kitchen complete w/gleaming SS appliances, recessed lighting, white cabinets w/crown moulding, a prep island, a breakfast bar, & a bay window in the breakfast nook. The main bedroom is a true retreat, w/ double-door entry, plush carpet, sitting area, & an ensuite w/dual sinks. In the grassy backyard, you'll find a covered patio & mature shade trees.
